====== Blog Plugin for DokuWiki ======

All documentation for the Blog Plugin is available online at:
http://www.wikidesign.ch/en/plugin/blog/start
http://wiki.splitbrain.org/plugin:blog

This plugin requires DokuWiki 2006-11-06 or later and these helper plugins:

  * Include Plugin   http://www.wikidesign.ch/en/plugin/include/start
  * Pagelist Plugin  http://www.wikidesign.ch/en/plugin/pagelist/start

There's a Google Groups mailing list to discuss all issues:
http://groups-beta.google.com/group/blog-plugin/

